1
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:55,620
Father.

2
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,900
I brought some food and wine you like.

3
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,650
This is your favorite wine.

4
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,500
This might be the last meal

5
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:19,200
I'll ever have with you.

6
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:47,079
Father.

7
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:51,530
Why did the Late Emperor assassinate Mother and my brother?

8
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:54,640
He was suspicious by nature.

9
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:59,000
The Xiao Army had become too powerful.

10
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,360
With them gone,

11
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:04,700
you became the only daughter of the Xiao family.

12
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,640
To the Li Imperial Family,

13
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:09,090
you were no longer a threat.

14
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,800
But Father,

15
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:13,410
how did you find out about this?

16
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:14,890
All these years,

17
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:18,640
I've been tracking those murderous bandits,

18
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,640
but found nothing.

19
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,600
Until two years ago,

20
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:24,720
when I received a secret letter.

21
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:25,760
It was the secret order from back then,

22
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:29,200
from the Late Emperor to the Xuan Bird Department to assassinate them.

23
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:30,200
Two years ago?

24
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:33,880
Why didn't you tell me then?

25
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:36,720
You were determined to marry Li Yunxi then.

26
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,160
If I had told you,

27
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,760
what could you have done?

28
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:42,680
No wonder.

29
00:03:44,079 --> 00:03:46,940
No wonder you wouldn't let me marry into the palace.

30
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:50,560
I, Xiao Rushan, have never failed my country.

31
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,970
But I have failed my wife and children.

32
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:56,260
Since the Late Emperor was cruel,

33
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,720
I will kill his son.

34
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:02,380
But he is not the Late Emperor.

35
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,330
I, Xiao Rushan, have no daughter like you.

36
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,480
Get out!

37
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,040
Father.

38
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,930
Please forgive me for being unfilial.

39
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,890
I'll repay you in the next life.

40
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,000
Li Yunxi.

41
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:33,080
The late Emperor killed my mother and brother.

42
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,080
A son must pay his father's debt.

43
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,040
I should kill you.

44
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,680
My father seeks revenge,

45
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,760
and wants to kill you.

46
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,760
You should kill him.

47
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:49,409
But between you and Father,

48
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,970
I don't want to hurt either.

49
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,280
If one of us has to die,

50
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,360
let it be me.

51
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:58,280
After I die,

52
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,600
let Father retire.

53
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,740
Let him go to Jiangnan.

54
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,890
Jiangnan is a lovely place.

55
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,740
If there is a next life,

56
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,920
I want to go there too.

57
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:13,480
We'll go...

58
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:15,880
together.

59
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,520
What I have done

60
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,920
has nothing to do with Xiao Ling.

61
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,920
General, go in peace.

62
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:35,440
His Majesty will treat the Empress well.

63
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:01,640
Father.

64
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:04,440
Father.

65
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,540
Your Highness, you're awake.

66
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,600
What is going on?

67
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:13,040
His Majesty knew you'd do something foolish,

68
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,440
so he secretly ordered me

69
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:15,700
to switch your poison.

70
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:17,170
You simply fell asleep.

71
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,240
If I didn't die,

72
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,540
what about Father?

73
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:38,760
Why?

74
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,440
Why, after all I've done,

75
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:44,400
could I still not save you?

76
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:49,360
Why wouldn't he let him go?

77
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,780
Your Highness,

78
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:53,760
let me escort the General out of the palace.

79
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,800
He is already dead.

80
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:57,880
Where are you taking him?

81
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,100
Your Highness.

82
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:01,280
His Majesty handled this secretly

83
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:03,400
to preserve the General's loyal name

84
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,300
and protect the Xiao Army's reputation.

85
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,280
For the sake of the Xiao Army,

86
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:10,720
please do not stop me.

87
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,880
Li Yunxi.

88
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:23,440
Why did you want my father dead?

89
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:27,240
Wasn't my life enough to exchange for his?

90
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:30,520
Which side is the real you?

91
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,060
Here, take it back.

92
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:41,050
If you want to hate someone,

93
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,560
hate me.

94
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:45,960
You killed my father,

95
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:49,920
and you expect me to pretend nothing happened,

96
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,970
and just keep on living?

97
00:07:58,520 --> 00:08:01,180
From today on, we are no longer husband and wife.

98
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:05,120
You can go anywhere you want.

99
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:10,040
I couldn't ask for more.

100
00:08:10,840 --> 00:08:13,370
I don't want to see you ever again in this life.

101
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:16,960
Ah Ling.

102
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,330
Jiangnan is a wonderful place.

103
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,960
If you like it,

104
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:30,720
go see it for me.

105
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,120
If you want to go,

106
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,360
go yourself.

107
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,520
If there is an afterlife,

108
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,400
let's go together.

109
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,880
You're crazy.

110
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:04,840
Ah Ling,

111
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,080
you are finally free.

112
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:12,200
Let me do one last thing for you.

113
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:22,840
Lord Su, you can stop here.

114
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,100
Please go back.

115
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:36,880
Father.

116
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:39,520
Father.

117
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:41,760
Father.

118
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:47,560
Young lady,

119
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,080
do you know who I am?

120
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,120
And where is this?

121
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,250
What did you say?

122
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:54,960
Master,

123
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:56,920
you just woke up. Don't run around.

124
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:58,320
We must return to Jiangnan immediately.

125
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,200
We can't delay.

126
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:02,320
Right. Let's go back.

127
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:03,940
Ling'er is waiting for me.

128
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:05,720
Come.

129
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:15,130
Why are you wearing a stealth suit at home?

130
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:17,250
Were you bullied in the palace?

131
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,040
You did this.

132
00:10:42,280 --> 00:10:43,080
Thank you,

133
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:44,560
Yunxi.

134
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:52,090
What is going on?

135
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:53,450
His Majesty said

136
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:55,280
the General is a meritorious subject

137
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:56,800
who deserves a good ending.

138
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:58,920
He used medicine to erase his memory

139
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:00,520
so he could retire

140
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,620
and live out his days in peace.

141
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:04,120
Why didn't he tell me this?

142
00:11:04,880 --> 00:11:07,010
He knew you were unhappy in the palace,

143
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:09,600
so he let you go do what you like.

144
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,460
Whether you follow the General to Jiangnan,

145
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:14,970
return to the Xiao Army,

146
00:11:15,760 --> 00:11:16,890
or wander the world,

147
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:19,640
His Majesty respects your wishes.

148
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:23,920
He was thinking of me until the very end.

149
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:25,960
Thank you.

150
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:30,320
A-Ling,

151
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:31,960
by now,

152
00:11:32,560 --> 00:11:33,760
you and General Xiao

153
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:35,570
must be on your way to Jiangnan.

154
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,730
Take good care of yourself.

155
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:39,210
In the next life,

156
00:11:39,920 --> 00:11:41,180
I won't be the Emperor.

157
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:44,240
I will definitely go with you.
